00:45:15.630 --> 00:45:20.070
"Yes, I know, I recognize Mother, yes, I know She is great,

00:45:20.271 --> 00:45:26.310
but I can't help it I have to tell Her lies".

00:45:26.873 --> 00:45:32.094
Or, "I have to do this wrong thing, because after all,

00:45:32.295 --> 00:45:38.250
ah - I can't help it." There is no compromise with Me.

00:45:38.451 --> 00:45:40.867
It has to be completely integrated.

00:45:41.068 --> 00:45:46.289
Your Dharma should be corrected. You can not do anything wrong

00:45:46.490 --> 00:45:49.367
and then say, "I'm a Sahaja Yogi." You cannot.

00:45:49.568 --> 00:45:53.859
But for this, the strength comes from within.

00:45:54.060 --> 00:45:56.060
Your Spirit strengthens you.

00:45:56.261 --> 00:46:01.474
You must just put in your will-power that "Yes, let my Spirit act."

00:46:01.675 --> 00:46:05.912
And then you start acting according to the Spirit.

00:46:06.113 --> 00:46:09.857
Once you start acting according to the Spirit,

00:46:10.058 --> 00:46:13.435
you find you have no slavery of anything.

00:46:13.636 --> 00:46:18.029
You become Samarth, means equal to your meanings.

00:46:18.230 --> 00:46:22.162
Samartha, also Samarth means powerful personality.

00:46:22.363 --> 00:46:25.303
So, you develop that powerful personality

00:46:25.504 --> 00:46:30.108
which has no temptations, which has no wrong ideas,

00:46:30.309 --> 00:46:35.434
which has no catches, no problems.

00:46:37.629 --> 00:46:42.287
But people who are sneaky, sly

00:46:42.488 --> 00:46:48.060
try to try, play some tricks are really harming themselves,

00:46:48.261 --> 00:46:52.083
not Sahaja Yoga. Sahaja Yoga is going to be,

00:46:52.284 --> 00:46:56.809
he has been and will be, is going to be established.

00:46:57.010 --> 00:47:02.457
Even if they are ten people in the boat, God is not bothered.

00:47:02.658 --> 00:47:05.840
It's only My botheration as a Mother.

00:47:06.041 --> 00:47:10.160
As a Mother, I want many people to come up in the boat.

00:47:10.361 --> 00:47:15.168
But don't try to jump back by doing all dishonest things.

00:47:15.369 --> 00:47:19.856
So, this is what it is - simple, that you are integrated.

00:47:20.057 --> 00:47:26.106
By integration, you get the power to do what you understand,

00:47:26.307 --> 00:47:32.012
and you have power to feel happy with what you understand.

00:47:32.213 --> 00:47:37.223
So, you come to a stage where you develop this Neerananda.

00:47:37.424 --> 00:47:39.770
And this Neeranand you develop

00:47:39.971 --> 00:47:45.278
when you are absolutely the Spirit.

00:47:45.479 --> 00:47:51.911
In Neerananda state there is no duality left -

00:47:52.112 --> 00:47:56.200
is Adwaita, is one personality.

00:47:56.401 --> 00:47:59.380
That is, you are complete integrated

00:47:59.581 --> 00:48:08.848
and the joy is not anymore dented - is complete.

00:48:09.168 --> 00:48:14.061
It hasn't got a happiness and a sorrow aspect,

00:48:14.262 --> 00:48:19.397
but is just Joy. The Joy is not that you laugh loud,

00:48:19.598 --> 00:48:26.702
the Joy is not that ah you you're always smiling. No,

00:48:26.903 --> 00:48:31.960
Is the stillness, the quietitude within your Self,

00:48:32.161 --> 00:48:36.593
the peace of your being, of your Spirit

00:48:36.794 --> 00:48:42.804
that asserts itself into vibrations which you feel,

00:48:43.005 --> 00:48:48.789
that when you feel that peace, you feel like light of the sun,

00:48:48.990 --> 00:48:52.281
the whole rays of that beauty spreading.

00:48:52.482 --> 00:48:55.297
But first of all we are curbed down

00:48:55.498 --> 00:49:00.875
by our own personal, selfish, stupid ideas.

00:49:01.076 --> 00:49:04.867
Throw them away! We have them because we are insecured,

00:49:05.068 --> 00:49:08.172
because we have wrong ideas, throw them away.

00:49:08.373 --> 00:49:12.961
Just stand alone, one with God.

00:49:13.162 --> 00:49:17.930
And you'll find all these fears were useless.

00:49:18.131 --> 00:49:21.477
Our cleansing is very important,

00:49:21.678 --> 00:49:26.930
and that cleansing comes only when you really practice

00:49:27.131 --> 00:49:31.834
the cleansing as told in Sahaja Yoga.

00:49:33.678 --> 00:49:38.750
The Sahastrara is the blessing of the heavens, I should say.

00:49:38.951 --> 00:49:41.945
It has worked out so well.

00:49:42.146 --> 00:49:44.859
It's very difficult to break the Sahastrara.

00:49:45.060 --> 00:49:48.461
And when I really broke it,

00:49:48.662 --> 00:49:53.102
I didn't know that it would be that successful.

00:49:53.303 --> 00:49:56.102
First, I thought is still premature

00:49:56.303 --> 00:50:02.055
because there are many Rakshasas still on the street,

00:50:02.256 --> 00:50:05.688
selling their goods; and there are many fanatics

00:50:05.889 --> 00:50:09.079
who are calling themselves by the so-called religions

00:50:09.280 --> 00:50:14.227
they are following, not the real religion of the Atma.

00:50:14.428 --> 00:50:19.047
But, gradually it has taken its roots.

00:50:19.248 --> 00:50:23.505
Now, let this truth take its root within yourself

00:50:23.706 --> 00:50:25.471
through your Sahasrara.

00:50:25.672 --> 00:50:31.656
And once this truth becomes absolutely the light that guides you,

00:50:31.857 --> 00:50:35.836
the light that nourishes you, the light that enlightens you

00:50:36.037 --> 00:50:40.938
and gives you a personality that has the light,

00:50:41.139 --> 00:50:43.860
then only you should know that your Sahastrara

00:50:44.061 --> 00:50:47.282
is completely enlightened by your Spirit.

00:50:47.483 --> 00:50:51.169
Your face should be such that people should know

00:50:51.370 --> 00:50:56.638
that there's a personality who's standing before you who is light.

00:50:56.839 --> 00:51:01.505
This is how Sahastrara is to be looked after.

00:51:01.706 --> 00:51:06.677
For looking after Sahastrara is is important that

00:51:06.878 --> 00:51:12.935
you should try to cover your head during winter time.

00:51:13.136 --> 00:51:16.201
Is better to cover your head during wintertime

00:51:16.402 --> 00:51:20.724
so that there is no freezing in the brain

00:51:20.925 --> 00:51:26.912
because brain is also made of Medha, means fats,

00:51:27.113 --> 00:51:30.435
so it should not be frozen. Moreover,

00:51:30.636 --> 00:51:34.294
you should not take too much heat on your brain.

00:51:34.495 --> 00:51:37.669
To keep your brain all right, you should not sit in the sun

00:51:37.870 --> 00:51:41.161
all the time as some of the Westerners do.

00:51:41.362 --> 00:51:47.557
Then your brain melts and you become a crazy person.

00:51:48.346 --> 00:51:54.442
Is a sign that a person is going out for madness -

00:51:54.643 --> 00:51:57.472
is something which I've told many a times

00:51:57.673 --> 00:52:01.488
that don't take too much heat on your head.

00:52:01.689 --> 00:52:05.683
Even if you are sitting in the sun, keep your head covered.

00:52:05.884 --> 00:52:09.399
Covering of the head is very important. But

00:52:09.600 --> 00:52:14.027
the covering of the head should be done occasionally,

00:52:14.228 --> 00:52:18.949
not all the time because if you just put

00:52:19.150 --> 00:52:23.243
a very heavy band around your head, then the circulation

00:52:23.444 --> 00:52:28.266
becomes poor and you may have trouble with bad circulation.

00:52:28.467 --> 00:52:36.610
So, it is an occasional opening of the head

00:52:36.811 --> 00:52:42.805
to the sun and to the moon, occasionally.

00:52:43.006 --> 00:52:48.943
Otherwise, you will sit in the moon and land up in the lunatic asylum.

00:52:50.451 --> 00:52:55.773
Anything I tell you, you must know that in Sahaja Yoga,

00:52:55.974 --> 00:52:59.679
we have not to go to anything [Ati/Adhi ?].

00:52:59.880 --> 00:53:03.546
Even sitting in the water, some people will sit for 3 hours.

00:53:03.747 --> 00:53:07.505
I never said so. Only for ten minutes you have to sit,

00:53:07.706 --> 00:53:09.706
but with full heart.

00:53:09.907 --> 00:53:13.839
If I tell them anything, they'll go on doing it for 4 hours,

00:53:14.040 --> 00:53:16.808
there's no need do it for ten hours.

00:53:17.009 --> 00:53:21.269
Give your body different-different types of treatments,

00:53:21.470 --> 00:53:24.711
not all the time the same treat. The body gets bored

00:53:24.912 --> 00:53:30.758
or gets absolutely ah - overburdened.

00:53:30.959 --> 00:53:33.758
Now, if you tell somebody, "this is your mantra".

00:53:33.959 --> 00:53:37.151
All right, it is to be used till you get rid of your Chakras,

00:53:37.352 --> 00:53:39.352
finished.

00:53:39.561 --> 00:53:42.618
Lo, something, some screw is to be put here; all right;

00:53:42.819 --> 00:53:45.454
now what you do - you put the screw till it fixes,

00:53:45.655 --> 00:53:47.655
you do not go on even when it is fixed.

00:53:47.856 --> 00:53:52.499
Are you going to screw it more and more

00:53:52.700 --> 00:53:56.640
so that ah - the whole thing gets spoiled?

00:53:56.841 --> 00:54:01.085
Is better that use wisdom. And for this wisdom,

00:54:01.286 --> 00:54:08.671
we must know that it is Shri Ganesha or Jesus Christ

00:54:08.872 --> 00:54:12.038
who are placed on both the sides. Here is Mahaganesha,

00:54:12.239 --> 00:54:13.942
here is Jesus Christ.

00:54:14.143 --> 00:54:20.181
Both of Them help you to correct your vision,

00:54:20.382 --> 00:54:22.704
understanding and give you wisdom.

00:54:22.905 --> 00:54:27.017
So, the wisdom lies not in sticking on to something.

00:54:27.218 --> 00:54:29.486
Sahaja Yogis are not stuck-up people.

00:54:29.687 --> 00:54:33.603
If they are stuck up, they are not progressing.

00:54:33.804 --> 00:54:36.353
You are not to get stuck up with ideas

00:54:36.554 --> 00:54:38.194
and stuck up with things.

00:54:38.395 --> 00:54:42.350
You have to be all the time moving and in the movement,

00:54:42.551 --> 00:54:46.156
it doesn't mean that you should fall from somewhere

00:54:46.357 --> 00:54:49.062
and people think, "Oh, we are earning such a lot,

00:54:49.263 --> 00:54:52.010
because we are falling down." You have to ascend

00:54:52.211 --> 00:54:54.916
in your movement, not to fall.

00:54:55.117 --> 00:54:58.213
So, when you are achieving something in Sahaja Yoga,

00:54:58.414 --> 00:55:01.916
first of all you should see your health should be all right.

00:55:02.117 --> 00:55:05.213
Your mind should be normal. You should be a normal person.

00:55:05.414 --> 00:55:07.760
If you are still barking at people,

00:55:07.961 --> 00:55:09.961
then know that there's something wrong with you.

00:55:10.162 --> 00:55:14.719
Or if you are still sulking and still tantrumish

00:55:14.920 --> 00:55:19.039
and if you are still in a bad mood,

00:55:19.240 --> 00:55:23.320
then think you are not yet a Sahaja Yogi. You can judge yourself,

00:55:23.521 --> 00:55:27.586
if you are free like a bird then it's all right.

00:55:27.787 --> 00:55:29.874
But that doesn't mean on the road you start singing

00:55:30.075 --> 00:55:32.530
like a bird and jumping on a tree.

00:55:32.731 --> 00:55:36.155
You see, any analogy I give to a stupid man,

00:55:36.356 --> 00:55:40.827
he can behave in a very stupid way. But to a wise man,

00:55:41.028 --> 00:55:44.749
he discreetly uses it for a proper purpose.

00:55:44.950 --> 00:55:48.374
So, one has to understand, Sahaja Yoga is

00:55:48.575 --> 00:55:53.465
known by the discretion person has.

00:55:54.661 --> 00:56:00.624
Now, what happens actually that you get stuck with one thing,

00:56:00.825 --> 00:56:05.172
that is your Atma and the whole your being

00:56:05.373 --> 00:56:11.906
floats like a [SOUNDS LIKE Patangas ?] does, or ah a kite that floats,

00:56:12.107 --> 00:56:14.274
goes all over the places, everything,

00:56:14.475 --> 00:56:18.547
but you are stuck to only one thing, that is your Spirit.

00:56:18.748 --> 00:56:25.422
And, if you could really do it, genuinely and honestly,

00:56:25.623 --> 00:56:30.102
not worry too much about your money and your families

00:56:30.303 --> 00:56:35.586
and other mundane things, just don't worry about anything,

00:56:35.787 --> 00:56:38.195
you don't have to worry, just give it a bandhan.

00:56:38.396 --> 00:56:40.396
If it doesn't work out, doesn't work out, finished.

00:56:40.597 --> 00:56:45.198
What's that wrong? If it works out, well and good.

00:56:45.785 --> 00:56:49.701
Not that your desire is important, but, "Thy will be done".

00:56:49.902 --> 00:56:52.123
First you say, "Thy will be done"

00:56:52.324 --> 00:56:55.326
that it is so surprising that your wills change,

00:56:55.527 --> 00:56:59.724
your desires change and whatever you say, is done.

00:56:59.925 --> 00:57:03.763
But when this also comes up, people develop an ego;

00:57:03.964 --> 00:57:09.794
so be careful. It's all done by the Shakti and not by you,

00:57:09.995 --> 00:57:15.121
by your Atma and not by you. You have to be the Atma

00:57:15.322 --> 00:57:18.394
and once you become the Atma, you become into Akarma

00:57:18.595 --> 00:57:21.957
where you don't know that you are doing it, it just works out.

00:57:22.158 --> 00:57:26.191
You don't feel, you are not aware.

00:57:26.392 --> 00:57:30.238
I wish, after all these lectures,

00:57:30.439 --> 00:57:34.527
most of your Chakras must have been opened.

00:57:34.728 --> 00:57:42.011
But this is all My work. You have to also do some homework.

00:57:42.212 --> 00:57:47.027
And, you have to also work and see for yourself. Be alert.

00:57:47.228 --> 00:57:51.011
Try to face yourself in the mirror and see for yourself

00:57:51.212 --> 00:57:54.464
how far honest you have become.

00:57:54.665 --> 00:57:56.956
How far clean have you been.

00:57:57.157 --> 00:58:00.050
How far friendly you are in collectivity -

00:58:00.251 --> 00:58:03.073
which is a very important point in Sahaja Yoga.

00:58:03.274 --> 00:58:09.206
If you are not collective, if you are funny, if you are strange,

00:58:09.407 --> 00:58:15.125
if you cannot communicate with others, then something wrong.

00:58:17.260 --> 00:58:24.341
And then you should face yourself as you are and try to correct it.

00:58:24.542 --> 00:58:26.542
Because you separate yourself from yourself

00:58:26.743 --> 00:58:30.261
like I separate My sari from Myself and try to clean it.

00:58:30.462 --> 00:58:34.089
In the same way, you separate yourself from yourself

00:58:34.290 --> 00:58:39.612
and try to clean it. This is the way Sahaja Yogis are going to ascend.

00:58:39.813 --> 00:58:41.813
When the Sahaja Yogis will ascend,

00:58:42.014 --> 00:58:44.391
the rest of the things also will ascend.

00:58:44.592 --> 00:58:50.618
Many Sahaja Yogis of this kind will impress so many people

00:58:50.819 --> 00:58:55.063
that they will also ascend. So, the whole thing can ascend very fast.

00:58:55.264 --> 00:58:58.688
But you people who are rising higher should try to rise

00:58:58.889 --> 00:59:01.774
higher and higher without being aware of it -

00:59:01.975 --> 00:59:05.810
that's very important.

00:59:06.889 --> 00:59:11.579
Those who are also who think that others are higher than them

00:59:11.780 --> 00:59:14.556
are also sadly mistaken, because that's not so.

00:59:14.757 --> 00:59:16.986
It's the whole that's rising.

00:59:17.187 --> 00:59:21.634
Nobody should feel that way inferior or in anyway low

00:59:21.835 --> 00:59:25.322
or feel insulted that somebody thinks we low.

00:59:25.523 --> 00:59:29.049
Let somebody think, what does it matter, Divine doesn't think so.

00:59:29.250 --> 00:59:33.135
So, all these little- little things you should be careful about,

00:59:33.336 --> 00:59:37.705
and otherwise it's very easy in this Krita Yuga

00:59:37.906 --> 00:59:44.228
achieve the ultimate goal of Atma Sakshatkar.

00:59:44.429 --> 00:59:48.650
I think today I have told you quite a lot about Sahastrara

00:59:48.851 --> 00:59:52.830
but if you have any problem about Sahastrara you may ask Me now

00:59:53.031 --> 00:59:55.768
but only about Sahastrara and nothing else, is better

00:59:55.969 --> 01:00:00.859
to ask Me questions about Sahastrara instead of all other things.

01:00:04.923 --> 01:00:08.220
You can ask Me questions.

