01:00:53.676 --> 01:00:57.577
Samadhi, Bindu, this, that, all that. Now please forget it,

01:00:57.778 --> 01:01:01.375
please forget all these things. Sama-dhi, Samadhi means,

01:01:01.576 --> 01:01:05.594
first is the Nirvichara Samadhi. First is Nirvichara Samadhi

01:01:05.795 --> 01:01:09.242
that you achieve and the Kundalini just comes out of your head.

01:01:09.443 --> 01:01:12.273
Sama-dhi means, the dhi means the buddhi.

01:01:12.474 --> 01:01:15.929
