01:01:16.130 --> 01:01:18.799
So first of all, the buddhi gets enlightened - I just now

01:01:19.000 --> 01:01:22.112
I told you about that only, the first enlightenment.

01:01:22.313 --> 01:01:25.354
Now, the Bindu and this and that are higher stages.

01:01:25.555 --> 01:01:28.588
Ardha Bindu,

01:01:28.789 --> 01:01:34.440
then Bindu and then Valaya. But you should not be futuristic,

01:01:34.641 --> 01:01:37.210
 just now if you have read some book no use

01:01:37.411 --> 01:01:39.577
trying to show off that. That's not a good thing.

01:01:39.778 --> 01:01:43.694
Just try to see what you are. Why do you want to talk about

01:01:43.895 --> 01:01:46.389
things which - which do not concern at this stage?

01:01:46.590 --> 01:01:50.381
Just now, supposing you are going by bullock cart,

01:01:50.582 --> 01:01:52.582
why do you want to ask about the aeroplane?

01:01:52.783 --> 01:01:56.113
Just now you go by bullock cart, then you get into the train,

01:01:56.314 --> 01:01:59.972
then you get into the airplane. All right? One by one,

01:02:00.173 --> 01:02:02.456
not like this. Because you have read the book,

01:02:02.657 --> 01:02:05.651
 it's not doesn't mean that you are supposed to know everything.

01:02:05.852 --> 01:02:09.237
All these books are written by some sort of crankish fellows

01:02:09.438 --> 01:02:12.260
who have read something here and there and have put it down.

01:02:12.461 --> 01:02:15.494
But you must experience. I'm your Mother,

01:02:15.695 --> 01:02:18.229
so I don't want to give you big ideas, this and that.

01:02:18.430 --> 01:02:23.127
I want you to do the way we have to move. As a mother would say,

01:02:23.328 --> 01:02:26.807
"Now, this is the way you are. Now you are in the first class,

01:02:27.008 --> 01:02:30.877
so pass your first exam. Then you'll go into the second class,

01:02:31.078 --> 01:02:32.382
then pass your exam".

01:02:32.583 --> 01:02:36.234
Everybody has to go that way to mature properly;

01:02:36.435 --> 01:02:39.007
there should be no immaturity in a personality.

01:02:39.208 --> 01:02:42.452
So all these books that you have read you better throw them away,

01:02:42.653 --> 01:02:45.389
there's no good. But if it is by some realized souls

01:02:45.590 --> 01:02:49.116
you can keep them and think that they are higher people

01:02:49.317 --> 01:02:52.608
and we have to be at their stage.

01:02:52.809 --> 01:02:57.217
Only by reading the book you don't become those personalities, do you?

